PURPOSE

emeraLD is tool to efficiently query and calculate linkage disequilibrium (LD) in large data sets 

it is ideal for rapid on-the-fly calculations, e.g. in GWAS analysis

--------------------------

supported data formats are currently VCF and M3VCF

see example.sh or run with --help for example usage

please send bug reports or other requests to corbinq@gmail.com

--------------------------
INSTALLATION

to install with libStatGen already present:
     cd emeraLD
     make LIBSTATGEN_PATH=my/path/to/libStatGen

to install without libStatGen:
     cd emeraLD
     make cloneLib
     make
     
